      .row
        .col-lg-8.mx-auto
          h2 About Mechsite
          p MechSite is a web retailer for mechanical keyboard switches based in Finland.
          p We offer great customer service and great shipping time and cost in EU.
          p Our store contains the hottest items in keyboard switches and accessories.
  section#contact.download-section.content-section.text-center(style='background-image: url("/images/Modifiedkailh.jpg");')
    .container
      .col-lg-8.mx-auto
        h2(style='font-size: 35px;text-transform: none;font-family: Lora, serif;') Contact us if you have any questions
        p
        button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-default(type='button') Contact
